verbose_text: As indicated in Figures XREF_FIG B and XREF_FIG C, PC3 cells incubated with scAb PSCA -Dtxl / SPIO-NPs produced distinct darkened regions in the T2 weighted MRI compared to the polymeric vesicles without scAb PSCA or Endorem (R) (a commercial contrast, Guerbet, France).
evidence: PC3 cells incubated with scAb PSCA -Dtxl/SPIO-NPs produced distinct darkened regions in the T2-weighted MRI
